     C**************************************************************************
** CMD
CLRPFM QTEMP/ALIWP30
** ERR
DATE IS REQUIRED.
DATE ERROR
FROM DATE > TODAY'S DATE.
NO DATA FOUND!
DATA OVER LIMIT! CHANGE SELECT CONDITION THEN TRY AGAIN.
PAGE# VALID WITH LOT#.




